languages.text: {n}Идира криво усмехается.{/n} "Я просто стала собой, Касс. Обычной серой мышкой, без придури и сожителей в дурной голове".
{n}Idira chuckles wryly.{/n} "I just became myself, Cass. Boring old me — a little grey mouse with no streak of madness in her, and no squatters living in her witless head."

languages.text: {n}イディラは不敵に笑う。{/n}「私はようやく元の自分に戻ったのよ、キャス。退屈なかつての私に…一片の狂気もなく、愚かな頭の中に勝手に居座るヤツもいない、小さな灰色のネズミに」
languages.original_text: {n}Idira chuckles wryly.{/n} "I just became myself, Cass. Boring old me — a little grey mouse with no streak of madness in her, and no squatters living in her witless head."

traits.locale_text: {n}イディラは不敵に笑う。{/n}「私はようやく元の自分に戻ったのよ、カシア。以前の私に。狂気…それとも私の疲れた頭の中に家賃なしで暮らすルームメイトとでも言うのかしら。それのいない、タダの灰入れのネズミにね」

languages.text: {n}伊迪拉咯咯地笑了起来。{/n}“我只是变回了我自己，小卡，从前那个无聊的我。像只小老鼠一样，没有疯疯癫癫的迹象，也没有叽叽喳喳的疯子挤在她愚蠢的脑袋里面。”
languages.original_text: {n}Idira chuckles wryly.{/n} "I just became myself, Cass. Boring old me — a little grey mouse with no streak of madness in her, and no squatters living in her witless head."

traits.locale_text: {n}伊迪拉咯咯地笑了起来。{/n}“我只是变回了我自己，小卡。普普通通的我，没有任何特别之处，脑子里也不再有一群叽叽喳喳的疯子强行挤在里面。”

languages.text: {n}Idira se ríe con sorna.{/n} «Acabo de convertirme en mí misma, Cass. La aburrida de siempre, una chica modosita sin ningún rastro de locura ni voces haciendo de okupas en una mente vacía».
languages.original_text: {n}Idira chuckles wryly.{/n} "I just became myself, Cass. Boring old me — a little grey mouse with no streak of madness in her, and no squatters living in her witless head."

traits.locale_text: {n}Idira se ríe con sorna.{/n} «Acabo de convertirme en mí misma, Cass. Mi yo de siempre, una chica normalita sin ningún rastro de locura ni voces viviendo en mi agotada mente».

languages.text: {n}Idira lacht trocken.{/n} "Ich bin gerade ich selbst geworden, Cass. Ich bin wieder ganz die langweilige Alte ... eine kleine graue Maus ohne einen Hauch von Wahnsinn oder unerwünschten Bewohnern in ihrem geistlosen Kopf."
languages.original_text: {n}Idira chuckles wryly.{/n} "I just became myself, Cass. Boring old me — a little grey mouse with no streak of madness in her, and no squatters living in her witless head."

traits.locale_text: {n}Idira lacht trocken.{/n} "Ich bin gerade ich selbst geworden, Cass. Mein gutes altes Selbst, eine graue Maus ohne den kleinsten Hauch von Wahnsinn, ohne Mitbewohner, die mietfrei in meinem erschöpften Oberstübchen wohnen."

languages.text: {n}Idira ricane.{/n} « Je n'ai fait que devenir moi-même, Cass, {n}répond-elle avec ironie.{/n} C'est toujours moi, la souris grise, mais sans le grain de folie ni les squatteurs dans mon esprit stupide. »
languages.original_text: {n}Idira chuckles wryly.{/n} "I just became myself, Cass. Boring old me — a little grey mouse with no streak of madness in her, and no squatters living in her witless head."

languages.text: {n}İdira, alaycı bir şekilde kıkırdıyor.{/n} "Kendim oldum işte Cass. Eski, sıkıcı hâlim bu... İçinde bir parça bile delilik olmayan, aptal kafasında başkalarının yaşamadığı, sıkıcı biriyim."
